rows.label: qev055804_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ah ha ha ha! That Tikotiko and his wacky Nopon
sense of humor! So so funny, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0002
rows.name:
Money exists to be spent, doesn't it?
Why would I just leave it lying around?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0003
rows.name:
I would be happy to share the pizza I bought with it,
but but I already ate all 25 of them. ...Sorry?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0006
rows.name:
I thought the Orphe were scary bad-guy types,
but Min'barac is very very friendly, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0007
rows.name:
Maybe he'll become a permanent member of our little
circle of ne'er-do-wells? I hope so, anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0008
rows.name:
Those amidresian tomatoes Min'barac wants grow
around Sayram Lake, I think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0009
rows.name:
I don't know all the details of what he is trying to do,
but but I hope he gets Selia's technique working.
Wouldn't that be great?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0010
rows.name:
Min'barac is very very smart, don't you think?
He memorized every word of what Selia told him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055804_MSG0011
rows.name:
He's on a different level from the rest of us forgetful
Ma-non, you know? It really is a a refreshing change.[ST:wait ]
